/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bobby-gillespie-paul-weller-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bobby-gillespie-paul-weller-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bobby-gillespie-paul-weller-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bobby-gillespie-paul-weller-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（12 月 13 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/primal-scream">Primal Scream</a>在 Brixton Academy <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primal-scream-paul-weller-and-kneecap-lead-gig-for-gaza-charity-show-line-up-at-brixton-academy-buy-tickets-3811809">Gig For Gaza</a>慈善演出中推出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-weller">Paul Weller</a>的《Rocks》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/primal-scream-bobby-gillespie-interview-come-ahead-3810374">原始尖叫在他们的抗议迪斯科专辑中：“如果你要从屋顶尖叫，没有比这更好的时机了”</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-jam">The Jam</a>前主唱 Weller 策划了这场慈善演出，该演出为<a href="https://www.map.org.uk/?form=emergency&amp;gad_source=1&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQiAlsy5BhDeARIsABRc6ZshNA22MX0BFpvgUHz5BR4cYOxeAmtOiGsQ586enESccucPYkD0I5gaAthOEALw_wcB" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MAP</a> （巴勒斯坦人医疗援助）和 Gaza Forever 筹集资金。两家慈善机构都为加沙当前人道主义危机中的受苦民众提供基本援助，包括食品、医疗用品和紧急住所。</p><p>在 Primal Scream 45 分钟的演出结束时，Weller 加入了他们的“Rocks”，用吉他演奏了这首歌标志性的开场即兴重复段。</p><p>查看下面的全套内容： </p><p><iframe title="Primal Scream ft Paul Weller - 在伦敦 O2 Brixton Academy 现场演出。 2024 年 12 月 13 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3xJPYNamt84?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>第二天，乐队在 Instagram 上感谢 Weller 和他的妻子 Hannah 组织了这场演出，同时也赞扬了其他表演的艺术家。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paloma-faith">Paloma Faith</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lowkey">Lowkey</a> 、Liam Bailey 和 Roisin El Cherif 也在阵容中。</p><p> “保罗和我们一起上台表演了一场喧闹的喷灯版本的《Rocks》，结束了整个活动——安德鲁·英尼斯 (Andrew Innes) 与 PW 同台时脸上的表情是无价的，”他们说。 “1977 年夏天，15 岁的安德鲁在格拉斯哥圣伊诺克广场的日瓦戈小俱乐部观看了 In The City 巡演中的 The Jam，那是当年的朋克表演之一，激发了安德鲁拿起吉他并组建乐队一支乐队。这真是一个多么美妙的夜晚啊。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDj3NOQOX1w/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.3